              This service is provided on an "as is" and "as available" basis. Future roadmap items
              are directional and may change.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-text">5. Contact</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Terms inquiries: <span class="text-text">legal@leter.net</span> (placeholder)
            </p>
